(xy)^{-1} = (xy)^{-1}\cdot e \cdot e
= (xy)^{-1}\cdot (xx^{-1})(yy^{-1})
= (xy)^{-1}\cdot (x)(x^{-1}\cdot y)(y^{-1})
= (xy)^{-1}\cdot (x)(y\cdot  x^{-1} )(y^{-1})
= (xy)^{-1}\cdot (x y)\cdot  (x^{-1} )(y^{-1})
= e \cdot x^{-1}  y^{-1}
=  x^{-1} y^{-1}
